    "Recall that more than one article is typically linked to a disclosure; the median is two.",
    "Applications: Reputation, privatization, and firm's use of scienceWe demonstrate the utility of our measure through two exercises.",
    "The first examines how universities' and researchers' reputations for producing commercializable science influence its use by21 Figures D.1, D.2, and D.3, in Online Appendix D, provide a visual interpretation of the results.",
